OOC: Actually Radiation wouldn't cause damage to the robots. Nor would it 
really amplify the powers of a stun beam.

The mysterious infecticon spun around as mutate attempted to fire at him, the 
chaochitan energy within its body increasing its speed. A second later the 
six small blue circles on his chest began to glow before launching six micro 
fusion beams at mutate.
